<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
@page {
  size: A4;
  margin: 2.2cm 2.5cm;
  @bottom-center { content: "Vertraulich — Cyber Aspis IT-Security"; font-size: 8pt; color: #9ca3af; }
  @bottom-right  { content: "Seite " counter(page) " von " counter(pages); font-size: 8pt; color: #9ca3af; }
}
@page cover { margin: 0; @bottom-center { content: none; } @bottom-right { content: none; } }

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.55; }

/* Cover */
.cover { page: cover; page-break-after: always; background: #0f172a; color: #f8fafc; width: 21cm; height: 29.7cm; padding: 3cm 3cm 2.5cm 3cm; }
.cover-logo { font-size: 22pt; font-weight: 800; color: #f8fafc; }
.cover-logo span { color: #34d399; }
.cover-tagline { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.cover-title-area { padding-top: 6cm; }
.cover-badge { display: inline-block; background: #064e3b; color: #34d399; border: 1px solid #34d399; font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.cover-title { font-size: 28pt; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.cover-subtitle { font-size: 14pt; color: #34d399; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.cover-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #334155; margin-bottom: 22px; }
.cover-meta-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.cover-meta-table td { padding: 0 20px 0 0; vertical-align: top; }
.cover-meta-label { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.cover-meta-value { font-size: 11pt; color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; }
.cover-footer { margin-top: 3.5cm; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; font-size: 8pt; color: #475569; line-height: 1.5; }

/* Headings */
h2 { font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; border-left: 4px solid #34d399; padding-left: 10px; margin: 26px 0 12px; page-break-after: avoid; }
h3 { font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin: 14px 0 6px; page-break-after: avoid; }

/* Tables */
.info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.info-table td { padding: 5px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: top; }
.info-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; width: 36%; color: #374151; white-space: nowrap; }

/* Status Boxes */
.sev-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 6px; margin: 14px 0; }
.sev-table td { text-align: center; padding: 10px 4px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
.sev-num { font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
.sev-lbl { font-size: 7.5pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; }
.box-green  { border-color: #6ee7b7 !important; background: #ecfdf5; }
.box-green .sev-num  { color: #059669; }
.box-yellow { border-color: #fcd34d !important; background: #fffbeb; }
.box-yellow .sev-num { color: #d97706; }
.box-red    { border-color: #fca5a5 !important; background: #fef2f2; }
.box-red .sev-num    { color: #dc2626; }
.box-gray   { border-color: #d1d5db !important; background: #f9fafb; }
.box-gray .sev-num   { color: #6b7280; }
.box-purple { border-color: #a78bfa !important; background: #f5f3ff; }
.box-purple .sev-num { color: #7c3aed; }
.box-blue   { border-color: #93c5fd !important; background: #eff6ff; }
.box-blue .sev-num   { color: #2563eb; }

/* Badges */
.badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 7.5pt; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; white-space: nowrap; }
.badge-critical { background: #f5f3ff; color: #7c3aed; border: 1px solid #a78bfa; }
.badge-high     { background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; border: 1px solid #fca5a5; }
.badge-medium   { background: #fffbeb; color: #d97706; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; }
.badge-low      { background: #ecfdf5; color: #059669; border: 1px solid #6ee7b7; }
.badge-info     { background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; border: 1px solid #93c5fd; }
.badge-resolved { background: #ecfdf5; color: #059669; border: 1px solid #6ee7b7; }
.badge-open     { background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; border: 1px solid #fca5a5; }
.badge-accepted { background: #f9fafb; color: #6b7280; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; }

/* Summary text */
.summary-text { font-size: 10.5pt; color: #374151; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 14px; }

/* Asset card */
.asset-card { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
.asset-card-header { background: #f8fafc; padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
.asset-card-header strong { font-size: 10pt; color: #0f172a; }
.asset-card-body { padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #4b5563; }

/* Finding rows in tables */
.findings-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 9pt; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.findings-table th { background: #0f172a; color: #f1f5f9; padding: 7px 9px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: 8.5pt; }
.findings-table td { padding: 6px 9px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; vertical-align: top; }
.findings-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #f9fafb; }

/* Section boxes */
.section-box { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 14px; overflow: hidden; }
.section-box-header { padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 700; }
.header-green  { background: #ecfdf5; color: #065f46; border-bottom: 2px solid #6ee7b7; }
.header-yellow { background: #fffbeb; color: #92400e; border-bottom: 2px solid #fcd34d; }
.header-red    { background: #fef2f2; color: #991b1b; border-bottom: 2px solid #fca5a5; }
.header-gray   { background: #f9fafb; color: #374151; border-bottom: 2px solid #d1d5db; }

/* Roadmap */
.roadmap-title { font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 700; padding: 7px 12px; }
.roadmap-sofort { background: #fef2f2; color: #991b1b; border: 1px solid #fca5a5; }
.roadmap-30     { background: #fffbeb; color: #92400e; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; }
.roadmap-90     { background: #eff6ff; color: #1e40af; border: 1px solid #93c5fd; }
.roadmap-table  { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.roadmap-table td { padding: 7px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-size: 9.5pt; vertical-align: top; }
.roadmap-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.roadmap-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
.roadmap-num { font-weight: 700; color: #6b7280; font-size: 9pt; width: 24px; white-space: nowrap; }
.roadmap-item-title { font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; }
.roadmap-item-rec   { color: #4b5563; font-size: 9pt; margin-top: 2px; }

/* Misc */
.page-break    { page-break-before: always; }
.no-data       { color: #9ca3af; font-style: italic; font-size: 9.5pt; }
.appendix-text { font-size: 9.5pt; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.success-bar   { background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #6ee7b7; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.warning-box   { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.field-label   { font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 2px; margin-top: 6px; }
.field-value   { color: #374151; line-height: 1.5; }
.field-mono    { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 8.5pt; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 5px 9px; border-radius: 3px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; color: #1e293b; }
.finding-card  { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.finding-header-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.finding-header-table td { padding: 8px 12px; vertical-align: middle; }
.fch-critical { background: #f5f3ff; border-bottom: 2px solid #a78bfa; }
.fch-high     { background: #fef2f2; border-bottom: 2px solid #fca5a5; }
.fch-medium   { background: #fffbeb; border-bottom: 2px solid #fcd34d; }
.fch-low      { background: #ecfdf5; border-bottom: 2px solid #6ee7b7; }
.fch-info     { background: #eff6ff; border-bottom: 2px solid #93c5fd; }
.finding-title { font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; }
.finding-card-body { padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 9.5pt; }
.finding-meta  { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
.finding-meta strong { color: #374151; }
.verified-badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 7.5pt; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 10px; background: #ecfeff; color: #0e7490; border: 1px solid #67e8f9; font-weight: 600; }
.cvss-val { font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700; font-family: monospace; }
.color-critical { color: #7c3aed; }
.color-high     { color: #dc2626; }
.color-medium   { color: #d97706; }
.color-low      { color: #059669; }
.color-info     { color: #2563eb; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

{# ═══════════════════════ DECKBLATT ═══════════════════════════════════════ #}
<div class="cover">
  <div class="cover-logo">Cyber <span>Aspis</span> IT-Security</div>
  <div class="cover-tagline">Your Digital Shield</div>

  <div class="cover-title-area">
    <div class="cover-badge">Abschlussbericht</div>
    <div class="cover-title">Security Assessment<br>Abschlussbericht</div>
    <div class="cover-subtitle">{{ customer.company_name }}</div>
    <hr class="cover-divider">
    <table class="cover-meta-table">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <div class="cover-meta-label">Auftraggeber</div>
          <div class="cover-meta-value">{{ customer.company_name }}</div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="cover-meta-label">Ansprechpartner</div>
          <div class="cover-meta-value">{{ customer.contact_person or '—' }}</div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="cover-meta-label">Assets geprüft</div>
          <div class="cover-meta-value">{{ assets|length }}</div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="cover-meta-label">Erstellt am</div>
          <div class="cover-meta-value">{{ generated_at }}</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-footer">
    Dieses Dokument enthält vertrauliche Sicherheitsinformationen und ist ausschließlich
    für den Auftraggeber bestimmt.<br>
    {% if customer.quote_number %}Angebotsnummer: {{ customer.quote_number }} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {% endif %}
    Projekt-Status: {{ customer.status }}
    {% if scans %}
     &nbsp;·&nbsp; Projektzeitraum: {{ scans[0].started_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if scans[0].started_at else '—' }}
     – {{ scans[-1].completed_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if scans[-1].completed_at else '—' }}
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>


{# ═══════════════════════ 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ════════════════════════════ #}
<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>

{% set open_count = counts.open + counts.in_progress %}
<p class="summary-text">
  Im Rahmen des Security Assessments für <strong>{{ customer.company_name }}</strong>
  wurden <strong>{{ assets|length }} Asset(s)</strong> über <strong>{{ scans|length }} Scan(s)</strong>
  geprüft. Dabei wurden insgesamt <strong>{{ counts.total }} Findings</strong> identifiziert
  ({{ counts.false_positives }} Falsch-Positive ausgeschlossen).

  {% if counts.resolved > 0 %}
  <strong style="color:#059669;">{{ counts.resolved }} Findings wurden behoben</strong> —
  {% endif %}
  {% if open_count == 0 and counts.accepted_risk == 0 %}
  das System ist vollständig abgesichert.
  {% elif open_count == 0 %}
  alle verbleibenden Risiken sind dokumentiert und akzeptiert.
  {% else %}
  <strong style="color:#dc2626;">{{ open_count }} Finding(s) sind noch offen</strong> und erfordern weitere Maßnahmen.
  {% endif %}
</p>

<table class="sev-table">
  <tr>
    <td class="box-green" ><div class="sev-num">{{ counts.resolved }}</div>     <div class="sev-lbl">Behoben</div></td>
    <td class="box-red"   ><div class="sev-num">{{ open_count }}</div>          <div class="sev-lbl">Noch offen</div></td>
    <td class="box-gray"  ><div class="sev-num">{{ counts.accepted_risk }}</div><div class="sev-lbl">Akzeptiert</div></td>
    <td class="box-purple"><div class="sev-num">{{ counts.critical }}</div>     <div class="sev-lbl">Critical</div></td>
    <td class="box-red"   ><div class="sev-num">{{ counts.high }}</div>         <div class="sev-lbl">High</div></td>
    <td class="box-yellow"><div class="sev-num">{{ counts.medium }}</div>       <div class="sev-lbl">Medium</div></td>
  </tr>
</table>

{% if open_count == 0 %}
<div class="success-bar">
  ✓ Alle aktiven Findings wurden behoben oder als akzeptiertes Risiko dokumentiert.
  Das System ist gemäß dem vereinbarten Scope abgesichert.
</div>
{% elif open_count > 0 %}
<div class="warning-box">
  <strong>Hinweis:</strong> Es sind noch {{ open_count }} Finding(s) offen.
  Bitte die Remediation Roadmap in Abschnitt 5 beachten.
</div>
{% endif %}


{# ═══════════════════════ 2. PROJEKT-ÜBERSICHT ═══════════════════════════ #}
<h2>2. Projekt-Übersicht</h2>

<table class="info-table">
  <tr><td>Auftraggeber</td>    <td>{{ customer.company_name }}</td></tr>
  {% if customer.contact_person %}<tr><td>Ansprechpartner</td><td>{{ customer.contact_person }}</td></tr>{% endif %}
  {% if customer.email          %}<tr><td>E-Mail</td>          <td>{{ customer.email }}</td></tr>{% endif %}
  {% if customer.quote_number   %}<tr><td>Angebotsnummer</td>  <td>{{ customer.quote_number }}</td></tr>{% endif %}
  <tr><td>Projekt-Status</td>  <td>{{ customer.status }}</td></tr>
  {% if scans %}
  <tr><td>Erster Scan</td>     <td>{{ scans[0].started_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if scans[0].started_at else '—' }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Letzter Scan</td>    <td>{{ scans[-1].completed_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if scans[-1].completed_at else '—' }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Anzahl Scans</td>    <td>{{ scans|length }}</td></tr>
  {% endif %}
  <tr><td>Assets geprüft</td>  <td>{{ assets|length }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Report erstellt</td> <td>{{ generated_at }}</td></tr>
</table>


{# ═══════════════════════ 3. GEPRÜFTE ASSETS & SCANS ════════════════════ #}
<h2>3. Geprüfte Assets &amp; Scans</h2>

{% for asset in assets %}
{% set asset_scans    = scans    | selectattr('asset_id', 'equalto', asset.id) | list %}
{% set asset_findings = findings | selectattr('asset_id', 'equalto', asset.id) | list %}
{% set asset_active   = asset_findings | rejectattr('false_positive') | list %}
<div class="asset-card">
  <div class="asset-card-header">
    <strong>{{ asset.value }}</strong>
    <span style="font-size:9pt; color:#6b7280; font-weight:normal;"> — {{ asset.asset_type }}</span>
    {% if asset.scope_authorized_by %}
    <span style="font-size:8.5pt; color:#059669; margin-left:8px;">✓ Autorisiert</span>
    {% else %}
    <span style="font-size:8.5pt; color:#d97706; margin-left:8px;">⚠ Kein Autorisierungsnachweis</span>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <div class="asset-card-body">
    <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:9pt;">

      {# Scope-Informationen #}
      {% if asset.scope_authorized_by %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:3px 12px 3px 0; color:#6b7280; white-space:nowrap; width:30%;">Autorisiert von</td>
        <td style="padding:3px 0; color:#374151;">
          {{ asset.scope_authorized_by }}
          {% if asset.scope_authorized_at %} am {{ asset.scope_authorized_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') }}{% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
      {% if asset.scope_valid_from and asset.scope_valid_until %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:3px 12px 3px 0; color:#6b7280;">Testzeitraum</td>
        <td style="padding:3px 0; color:#374151;">
          {{ asset.scope_valid_from.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') }} – {{ asset.scope_valid_until.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') }}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
      {% if asset.scope_notes %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:3px 12px 3px 0; color:#6b7280; vertical-align:top;">Scope-Vereinbarung</td>
        <td style="padding:3px 0; color:#374151;">{{ asset.scope_notes }}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}

      {# Trennlinie zwischen Scope und Scan-Infos #}
      <tr><td colspan="2" style="padding:4px 0;"><hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;"></td></tr>

      {# Scan-Übersicht #}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:3px 12px 3px 0; color:#6b7280;">Scans</td>
        <td style="padding:3px 0; color:#374151;">{{ asset_scans|length }} abgeschlossen</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:3px 12px 3px 0; color:#6b7280;">Findings</td>
        <td style="padding:3px 0;">
          {{ asset_active|length }} gesamt —
          <span style="color:#059669;">{{ asset_active | selectattr('status', 'equalto', 'resolved') | list | length }} behoben</span>,
          <span style="color:#dc2626;">{{ asset_active | selectattr('status', 'in', ['open', 'in_progress']) | list | length }} offen</span>,
          <span style="color:#6b7280;">{{ asset_active | selectattr('status', 'equalto', 'accepted_risk') | list | length }} akzeptiert</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% for s in asset_scans %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:2px 12px 2px 0; color:#9ca3af; font-size:8.5pt;">Scan #{{ s.id }}</td>
        <td style="padding:2px 0; font-size:8.5pt; color:#6b7280;">
          {{ s.scan_type }}
          {% if s.completed_at %} · {{ s.completed_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') }}{% endif %}
          {% if s.custom_ports %} · Ports: {{ s.custom_ports }}{% endif %}
          {% if s.scan_intensity %} · Intensität: {{ s.scan_intensity }}{% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
{% endfor %}


{# ═══════════════════════ 4. ALLE FINDINGS ═══════════════════════════════ #}
<h2>4. Findings — Gesamtübersicht</h2>

{% if findings %}

{# Behoben #}
{% if resolved %}
<div class="section-box">
  <div class="section-box-header header-green">✓ Behobene Findings ({{ resolved|length }})</div>
  <table class="findings-table">
    <thead><tr>
      <th style="width:36%">Titel</th>
      <th style="width:12%">Severity</th>
      <th style="width:30%">Asset</th>
      <th style="width:22%">Verifiziert von</th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for f in resolved %}
      <tr>
        <td style="font-weight:500;">{{ f.title }}{% if f.cve_id %} <span style="font-size:8pt;color:#9ca3af;">({{ f.cve_id }})</span>{% endif %}</td>
        <td><span class="badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span></td>
        <td style="font-size:9pt; color:#6b7280;">{{ asset_map[f.asset_id].value if f.asset_id in asset_map else '—' }}</td>
        <td style="font-size:9pt;">
          {% if f.verified_manually %}
          <span style="color:#059669;">✓ {{ f.verified_by or 'verifiziert' }}</span>
          {% else %}—{% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
{% endif %}

{# Akzeptiertes Risiko #}
{% if accepted %}
<div class="section-box">
  <div class="section-box-header header-gray">◎ Akzeptierte Risiken ({{ accepted|length }})</div>
  <table class="findings-table">
    <thead><tr>
      <th style="width:38%">Titel</th>
      <th style="width:12%">Severity</th>
      <th style="width:50%">Begründung / Notizen</th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for f in accepted %}
      <tr>
        <td style="font-weight:500;">{{ f.title }}</td>
        <td><span class="badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span></td>
        <td style="font-size:9pt; color:#6b7280; font-style:italic;">{{ f.notes or f.impact or '—' }}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
{% endif %}

{# Noch offen #}
{% if still_open %}
<div class="section-box">
  <div class="section-box-header header-red">⚠ Noch offene Findings ({{ still_open|length }})</div>
  <table class="findings-table">
    <thead><tr>
      <th style="width:36%">Titel</th>
      <th style="width:12%">Severity</th>
      <th style="width:18%">Asset</th>
      <th style="width:14%">Priorität</th>
      <th style="width:20%">Empfehlung (Kurzform)</th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for f in still_open %}
      <tr>
        <td style="font-weight:500;">{{ f.title }}</td>
        <td><span class="badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span></td>
        <td style="font-size:9pt; color:#6b7280;">{{ asset_map[f.asset_id].value if f.asset_id in asset_map else '—' }}</td>
        <td style="font-size:9pt;">
          {% if f.remediation_priority == 'SOFORT'   %}<span style="color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;">Sofort</span>
          {% elif f.remediation_priority == '30_TAGE' %}<span style="color:#d97706;">30 Tage</span>
          {% elif f.remediation_priority == '90_TAGE' %}<span style="color:#2563eb;">90 Tage</span>
          {% else %}—{% endif %}
        </td>
        <td style="font-size:8.5pt; color:#6b7280;">{{ (f.recommendation or '')[:80] }}{% if f.recommendation and f.recommendation|length > 80 %}…{% endif %}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% else %}
<p class="no-data">Keine Findings für diesen Kunden.</p>
{% endif %}


{# ═══════════════════════ 5. FINDINGS DETAIL ═════════════════════════════ #}
{% if findings %}
<div class="page-break"></div>
<h2>5. Findings Detail</h2>

{% macro finding_card(f) %}
<div class="finding-card">
  <table class="finding-header-table fch-{{ f.severity }}">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:auto; padding-right:6px;"><span class="badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span></td>
      <td style="width:100%;"><div class="finding-title">{{ f.title }}</div></td>
      {% if f.cvss_score is not none %}
      <td style="text-align:right; white-space:nowrap; padding-left:8px;">
        <span class="cvss-val color-{{ f.severity }}" style="font-size:13pt;">{{ "%.1f"|format(f.cvss_score) }}</span>
        <span style="font-size:7.5pt; color:#6b7280; display:block;">CVSS</span>
      </td>
      {% endif %}
    </tr>
  </table>
  <div class="finding-card-body">
    <div class="finding-meta">
      <strong>Asset:</strong> {{ asset_map[f.asset_id].value if f.asset_id in asset_map else '—' }} &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <strong>Quelle:</strong> {{ f.source }} &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <strong>Status:</strong>
      {% if f.status == 'open' %}Offen
      {% elif f.status == 'in_progress' %}In Bearbeitung
      {% elif f.status == 'resolved' %}Behoben
      {% elif f.status == 'accepted_risk' %}Akzeptiertes Risiko{% endif %}
      {% if f.cve_id %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>CVE:</strong> {{ f.cve_id }}{% endif %}
      {% if f.remediation_priority %} &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <strong>Priorität:</strong>
        {% if f.remediation_priority == 'SOFORT' %}Sofort
        {% elif f.remediation_priority == '30_TAGE' %}30 Tage
        {% elif f.remediation_priority == '90_TAGE' %}90 Tage{% endif %}
      {% endif %}
      {% if f.verified_manually %}
       &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="verified-badge">✓ Verifiziert{% if f.verified_by %} von {{ f.verified_by }}{% endif %}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if f.description and not f.impact %}
    <div class="field-label">Beschreibung</div><div class="field-value">{{ f.description }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if f.impact %}
    <div class="field-label">Auswirkung</div><div class="field-value">{{ f.impact }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if f.recommendation %}
    <div class="field-label">Empfehlung</div><div class="field-value">{{ f.recommendation }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if f.evidence %}
    <div class="field-label">Nachweis</div><div class="field-mono">{{ f.evidence }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if f.notes %}
    <div class="field-label">Notizen</div>
    <div class="field-value" style="color:#6b7280; font-style:italic;">{{ f.notes }}</div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>
{% endmacro %}

{% if still_open %}
<h3 style="color:#dc2626;">⚠ Noch offene Findings</h3>
{% for f in still_open %}{{ finding_card(f) }}{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if resolved %}
<h3 style="color:#059669; margin-top:20px;">✓ Behobene Findings</h3>
{% for f in resolved %}{{ finding_card(f) }}{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if accepted %}
<h3 style="color:#6b7280; margin-top:20px;">◎ Akzeptierte Risiken</h3>
{% for f in accepted %}{{ finding_card(f) }}{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% endif %}


{# ═══════════════════════ 7. REMEDIATION ROADMAP ═════════════════════════ #}
{% if roadmap_sofort or roadmap_30 or roadmap_90 %}
<div class="page-break"></div>
<h2>6. Remediation Roadmap — Noch offene Maßnahmen</h2>

<p class="summary-text">
  Die folgenden Maßnahmen sind noch ausstehend und sollten nach Priorität umgesetzt werden.
</p>

{% macro roadmap_block(items, css_class, label) %}
{% if items %}
<div class="roadmap-title {{ css_class }}">{{ label }} ({{ items|length }})</div>
<table class="roadmap-table">
  {% for f in items %}
  <tr>
    <td class="roadmap-num">{{ loop.index }}.</td>
    <td>
      <div class="roadmap-item-title">
        <span class="badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span>
        &nbsp;{{ f.title }}
        <span style="font-size:8.5pt; color:#6b7280;"> — {{ asset_map[f.asset_id].value if f.asset_id in asset_map else '' }}</span>
      </div>
      {% if f.recommendation %}
      <div class="roadmap-item-rec">{{ f.recommendation }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>
  {% endfor %}
</table>
{% endif %}
{% endmacro %}

{{ roadmap_block(roadmap_sofort, "roadmap-sofort", "⚡ Sofort — innerhalb 48 Stunden") }}
{{ roadmap_block(roadmap_30,     "roadmap-30",     "▲ Innerhalb 30 Tage") }}
{{ roadmap_block(roadmap_90,     "roadmap-90",     "● Innerhalb 90 Tage") }}
{% endif %}


{# ═══════════════════════ 8. ANHANG ══════════════════════════════════════ #}
<div class="page-break"></div>
<h2>7. Anhang</h2>

<h3>Projekthistorie — Scan-Übersicht</h3>
{% if scans %}
<table class="info-table">
  <tr>
    <td style="font-weight:700; background:#f8fafc;">Scan-ID</td>
    <td style="font-weight:700; background:#f8fafc;">Asset</td>
    <td style="font-weight:700; background:#f8fafc;">Typ</td>
    <td style="font-weight:700; background:#f8fafc;">Datum</td>
  </tr>
  {% for s in scans %}
  <tr>
    <td>#{{ s.id }}</td>
    <td>{{ asset_map[s.asset_id].value if s.asset_id in asset_map else '—' }}</td>
    <td>{{ s.scan_type }}</td>
    <td>{{ s.completed_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if s.completed_at else '—' }}</td>
  </tr>
  {% endfor %}
</table>
{% else %}
<p class="no-data">Keine abgeschlossenen Scans.</p>
{% endif %}

<h3>Verwendete Tools</h3>
<table class="info-table">
  <tr><td>Netzwerk-Scan</td>  <td>nmap — Portscanning, Service-Erkennung, OS-Fingerprinting</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Web-Analyse</td>    <td>nikto — HTTP-Server Schwachstellenscanner</td></tr>
  <tr><td>SSL/TLS-Analyse</td><td>testssl.sh — SSL/TLS-Konfiguration und Zertifikatsprüfung</td></tr>
  <tr><td>CVSS-Bewertung</td> <td>CVSS v3.1 — Manuelle Einstufung durch Analyst</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Haftungsausschluss</h3>
<p class="appendix-text">
  Dieser Abschlussbericht dokumentiert den Stand der Sicherheitsanalyse zum Zeitpunkt der
  letzten Prüfung. Neue Schwachstellen können jederzeit bekannt werden. Empfohlen wird
  eine regelmäßige Wiederholung (mindestens quartalsweise) sowie manuelle Penetrationstests
  für kritische Systeme. Cyber Aspis IT-Security übernimmt keine Haftung für Schäden durch
  die Implementierung der empfohlenen Maßnahmen.
</p>

</body>
</html>
